Emacs configuration files used on Mac OSX
GNU Emacs 23.2.1

Contents of the file ~/.emacs, which now just loads the file emacs.el
(formerly known as ~/.emacs) so it can be placed into the git
repository directory.

----------------------------------------

;;;_. -*-mode: emacs-lisp -*-
;; set to t for debugging
(setq debug-on-error nil)

;;; =====================================================================
;;; .emacs --- Emacs configuration file

;;; load the actual configuration file, located in emacs-pkgs to
;;; simplify version control
(load-file "~/emacs-pkgs/emacs.el")  ; emacs configuration

